 == empty %}<script type="text/plain" class="product-json" id="product-json{{product.id}}">{{ product | json }}</script>{% endunless %}{% endform %}{% endunless %}</product-form></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-8" id="c-1707204414039" data-id="1707204414039" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709215951389" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709215951389"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p></p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--font-body-family);">• When using <a href="https://www.koreanskincare.co.uk/collections/hair-care" class="">shampoo</a>, go for a double round —focus it only on your scalp. First round to get rid of the initial gunk, rinse it out. Then, hit it again, giving your scalp a good massage. This helps kick out any leftover oils and build-up. Rinse well, and let the shampoo slide down your hair for a gentle clean.&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--font-body-family);">• Use a hair mask in between shampooing and conditioning. Your hair is just like pores, namely they have scales. These hair scales open and close at different pH levels. On average, a shampoo has a pH value of 5.5. Combined with warm water, it causes the scales to open nicely for better washing of your hair. A conditioner is a lower pH value than a shampoo. This means that the hair cuticles close and a protective layer of conditioner comes over them. So when you want to apply a hair mask to your routine, it is important to use the mask between shampoo and conditioner. This is because then the hair cuticles are still open, so the product is better absorbed into your hair.</span><br><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--font-body-family);">• Use a conditioner and let it sit for 3-5 minutes. Think of it as a quick pampering session for your hair. Rinse it out, and voilà—hello, silky smooth locks!&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--font-body-family);">Give your hair the special treatment it deserves with a conditioning leave-in treatment or mask for a hydrating hit.</span><br><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709215951364" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709215951364" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709215951351" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709215951351"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Give Your Skin The Love It Needs&nbsp;</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709215951359" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709215951359"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><u>The Ultimate Booster:</u></span></p><p></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">In the realm of beauty, where radiant skin meets a flawless makeup canvas, the secret to a perfect look lies in the heart of Korean skincare. Let's embark on a K-Beauty journey to ensure your skin is not only cleansed to perfection but also prepped for a makeup look that will leave your date flabbergasted.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709215951336" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709215951336" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1707204262536" data-id="1707204262536" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709215951352" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709215951352"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">• Hydration boost</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Hydrated skin provides a smooth surface for makeup application and can prevent foundation from settling into fine lines or dry patches.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">• Priming effect&nbsp;</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Skin boosters can act as effective primers, creating a base that allows makeup to adhere more evenly to the skin. This can help your foundation and other makeup products go on more smoothly, ensuring a more flawless finish.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">• Enhanced Radiance</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Certain skin boosters contain ingredients that promote radiance and luminosity. These can contribute to a healthy and glowing complexion, adding a natural radiance to your makeup look.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">• Improving skin texture</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">&nbsp;Skin boosters often include ingredients that improve the texture of the skin. They can help refine pores, smooth out uneven areas, and create a more polished appearance, which translates into a more refined makeup application.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">• Longer lasting make-up</span><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">By providing a well-hydrated and primed base, skin boosters can contribute to the longevity of your makeup. Makeup tends to adhere better to well-moisturized skin, and a skin booster can help create a lasting makeup look throughout the day.</span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1707204264629" data-id="1707204264629" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1709215951365" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1709215951365" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-curr